title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - Top 5 busiest airports - Canada
description:
In this video we will look at the top 5 busiest airports in Canada. This top 5 contains 3 airports which have been updated by the community so a lot of details can be seen when visiting those airports.

00:00 intro
00:10 Edmonton International Airport (CYEG)
04:20 Montreal - Trudeau International Airport (CYUL)
12:04 Calgary International Airport (CYYC)
16:48 Vancouver International Airport (CYVR)
25:26 Toronto Pearson International Airport (CYYZ)
